      "input": "Content: Parameters\n--PlatformVersion same as with update.\n\n--DisableSecureInstall [true|<no input>]\n\nDisables secure platform install feature (Secure Platform feature is enabled by default in versions 7.4.0 and higher.\n\n--ProductionLevel [1-5|no input]\nSets the Production level of the system during an update or install. Default is 2 (development)\n\nExample\n./install.sh --PlatformVersion 8.23.1-GA --DisableSecureInstall true --ProductionLevel 5\nclear-cache.sh\nClears the platform cache, restart the application server and then check to make sure the Designer Studio is up and accessible after the restart.\n\nParameters\n--clear-database-cache\nClears the database cache tables as well as the system cache.\n\n--clear-cassandra-data\nClears Cassandra as well (used by CDH).\n\nExample\n./clear-cache.sh --clear-database-cache --clear-cassandra-data\nRestart\nThis operation will restart the application server and then check to make sure the Designer Studio is up and accessible after the restart."
